## Migration Guide

### Before (Ad-hoc Spacing)

```tsx
// ❌ OLD - Inconsistent spacing
<div className="p-3">  {/* Widget 1 uses p-3 */}
  <div className="space-y-2">  {/* 8px vertical spacing */}
    <ul className="space-y-4">  {/* 16px list spacing */}
      <li>Item 1</li>
      <li>Item 2</li>
    </ul>
    <button>Action</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div className="p-6">  {/* Widget 2 uses p-6 */}
  <div className="space-y-4">  {/* 16px vertical spacing */}
    <ul className="space-y-2">  {/* 8px list spacing */}
      <li>Item 1</li>
      <li>Item 2</li>
    </ul>
    <button>Action</button>
  </div>
</div>
```

**Problems:**
- Widget 1 padding (12px) ≠ Widget 2 padding (24px)
- Widget 1 list spacing (16px) ≠ Widget 2 list spacing (8px)
- No consistency across components

---

### After (Standardized Spacing)

```tsx
// ✅ NEW - Consistent spacing
<div className="p-4">  {/* ALWAYS p-4 */}
  <div className="space-y-4">  {/* ALWAYS space-y-4 for sections */}
    <ul className="space-y-3">  {/* ALWAYS space-y-3 for lists */}
      <li>Item 1</li>
      <li>Item 2</li>
    </ul>
    <button>Action</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div className="p-4">  {/* ALWAYS p-4 */}
  <div className="space-y-4">  {/* ALWAYS space-y-4 for sections */}
    <ul className="space-y-3">  {/* ALWAYS space-y-3 for lists */}
      <li>Item 1</li>
      <li>Item 2</li>
    </ul>
    <button>Action</button>
  </div>
</div>
```

**Benefits:**
- Widget padding: Always 16px
- Section spacing: Always 16px
- List spacing: Always 12px
- **Result:** Perfect visual harmony

