## Testing Checklist

When applying spacing standards to a component:

- [ ] Widget internal padding is `p-4` (16px)
- [ ] Content sections use `space-y-4` (16px)
- [ ] List items use `space-y-3` (12px)
- [ ] Button groups use `gap-2` (8px)
- [ ] No extra spacing beneath last element (removes "big gap" issue)
- [ ] Test in light mode
- [ ] Test in dark mode
- [ ] Test on mobile (375px)
- [ ] Test on tablet (768px)
- [ ] Test on desktop (1920px)
- [ ] Compare before/after screenshots (should match or improve)

