**Before:**
```tsx
<div className="p-3 bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-card">
  <div className="space-y-2">
    <h3 className="text-sm font-semibold mb-3">Tasks (3)</h3>
    <ul className="space-y-4">
      <li>Task 1</li>
      <li>Task 2</li>
      <li>Task 3</li>
    </ul>
