**Improvements:**
- ✅ Padding now standard (p-4 = 16px)
- ✅ Section spacing now standard (space-y-4 = 16px)
- ✅ List spacing now standard (space-y-3 = 12px)
- ✅ No extra bottom spacing (no "big gap")

